testcase.name: Test Case 1: Register User
testcase.system-out: 1. Launch browser 2. Navigate to url http://automationexercise.com 3. Verify that home page is visible successfully 4. Click on 'Signup / Login' button 5. Verify 'New User Signup!' is visible 6. Enter name and email address 7. Click Signup button 8. Verify that ENTER ACCOUNT INFORMATION is visible 9. Fill details: Title, Name, Email, Password, ... 10. Click Create Account button 11. Verify that ACCOUNT CREATED! is visible 12. Click Continue button 13. Verify that Logged in as username is visible 14. Click Delete Account button 15. Click Continue button 16. Verify that ACCOUNT DELETED! is visible
